						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Sundara Chōḻa-Pāṇḍya(?) Year 6 = 1027 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Fragment Seems to register a grant of kāṇikaḍaṉ from a devadana village Imānabharana chadurvēdimangalam. The seat in the palace hall <hi rend="italic">(kūḍam)</hi> from where the order was proclaimed was called RājendraChōḻa-Kārāṉai-viḷupparaiyan. Officers tirumantiravōlai, (Tirumuga)viḍai, paṭṭōlai and puravuvari are mentioned.</p>						

						<p>[Published in <hi rend="italic">SII.</hi> Vol. XIV, No. 133.]</p>						

						</summary>
